title: Hairball_-_A_Cal_McDonald_Mystery_(IDW_-_2002)_(Rumor-Novus-HD).
description:
Hairball_-_A_Cal_McDonald_Mystery_(IDW_-_2002)_(Rumor-Novus-HD) 


Cal McDonald's back in Hairball, collecting a four-part story that originally appeared in Dark Horse Presents. This time around, everybody's favorite private dick of the paranormal runs across a pack of wild teen werewolves that only Cal and his undead pals can stop. A one-shot issue written by Steve Niles (Savage Membrane: A Cal McDonald Mystery and Hellspawn) and illustrated by Casey Jones (Birds of Prey, Spider-Girl, Excalibur) and Bruce Patterson.
